column5: Hello all first... I would like to wish all a safe and Merry Christmas and a Happy New Year and hope the J-11 hooks are sharp.  I am looking for a place that would rent a utilty trailer as I want to get some firewood and get it to the cottage over the holidays... Would you know of a place other than U-haul!!!    Ken
Ken  Where do you live? I'm just south of Barie Ont, and I might be able to get access to my niece's utility trailer.
